# WHERE vs HAVING
==================


WHERE                          vs                 HAVING
filter rows                                  filter groups

applied before group by                      applied after group by

use where clause if condition                 use where clause if condition
doesn't contain group by                      doesn't contain group by

Note:-
-----
If condition contain group function use having clause,if condition not having group function use where clause


Q)Dept wise total salary where dept no=1,2

